window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>I spent 20 years waiting for Trent Hennington to open his eyes and see me. But it was all for nothing. He chose to keep himself guarded and let me walk away, proving that my time and efforts were wasted. </p> <p>I'm done being invisible. </p> <p>It's time to move on. </p> <p>A single dance sets my new reality into motion, and I welcome it. After all, Cooper Townsend is perfect. He's kind, sexy, and attentive - everything a girl could want. </p> <p>I thought I got it right this time. </p> <p>That my heart could mend, and I would be happy. </p> <p>Apparently, some things really are just too hard to walk away from. </p>"; 
